		      <section>
                        <hr align="left" width="900" size="5" noshade="noshade">
                        <h3 align='left'> Experimental setup </h3>
                        <hr align="left" width="900" size="5" noshade="noshade">
                        <!--                     LEFT COLUMN -->
			<div style="float:left;width:56%;font-size:30px;"> 
			<h6 align="left"> What happens after shockwave hits? </h6>
			<br>
			<ul>
			    <li> Changes in blood-brain barrier(BBB) diffusion. <br></br> </li>
			    <li> Damage to astrocytes cells. <br></br></li>
			    <li> Brain cells damage. <br></br> </li>
			</ul>
			<p align="left" style="font-size:30px">  Experimental setup done with BBB endothelial cells. </p>
			
